  "title": "Données du signal Ecowatt (à partir du 01/09/2022) JSON API",
  "description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Ce jeu de données présente l'historique du\nsignal Ecowatt au périmètre France depuis le 1er septembre 2022.  Il est rafraîchi une fois par jour, ainsi\nl'historique disponible le jour J contient les valeurs jusqu'au jour J-1. Il\ns'agit des derniers signaux Ecowatt publiés pour les 24 pas horaires (H0 à H23)\nde chaque jour.</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">A chacun des 24 pas horaires de la journée sont associés une valeur et un message texte. La valeur peut varier de 1 à 3. La signification des valeurs est la\nsuivante :</span><br></p><ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-fareast-language:FR'><b>0 : Signal Vert + Production décarbonée (*) - à partir du 3 novembre 2023</b></span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1 : Signal Vert</span>. Message associé : Pas d'alerte. Consommation normale.</span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-fareast-language:FR'><b>2 : Signal Orange</b>. Message associé : Le\n     système électrique est tendu. Les éco-gestes sont les bienvenus.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:#585858;mso-fareast-language:\n     FR'><b>3 : Signal Rouge</b>. Message associé : Le système électrique est très tendu. Coupures inévitables si nous ne baissons pas notre consommation. Adoptons tous les éco-gestes.</span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:#585858;mso-fareast-language:\nFR'><i>(*) La production d'électricité française émet déjà très peu de CO2 toute l'année. En privilégiant les heures décarbonnées pour consommer, la production française peut se rapprocher du 0 émission.</i></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:#585858;mso-fareast-language:\nFR'>A chaque jour est également associée une couleur du jour, celle-ci correspond à la valeur la plus élevée du signal sur l'ensemble des pas horaires de cette journée. Par exemple, il suffit d'un pas horaire orange (ou rouge) pour que la couleur du jour soit orange.(ou rouge).</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\">L'ensemble des informations associées au\nservice Ecowatt sont disponibles sur le site</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.monecowatt.fr/\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">www.monecowatt.fr</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">, <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">en particulier les prévisions en temps réel\npour les jours J à J+3. Pour récupérer en temps réel les données du signal\nEcowatt, RTE met à votre disposition une API publique sur </span></span><a href=\"https://data.rte-france.com/catalog/-/api/consumption/Ecowatt/v5.0\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Catalogue API - API Data RTE (rte-france.com)</a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><i style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nota : Le dispositif Ecowatt est exclusivement national puisque l'équilibre entre production et consommation d'électricité s'effectue à l'échelle nationale. Ainsi, la référence aux régions, présente dans les versions précédentes, disparait.</i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif; margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><i>Néanmoins, l'historique des signaux régionaux reste disponible sur le jeu de données suivant :</i> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://odre.opendatasoft.com/explore/dataset/signal-ecowatt/information/?disjunctive.region\"><span style='font-family: \"inherit\", serif;'>Données du signal écoWatt — Open Data Réseaux Énergies (ODRÉ) (opendatasoft.com)</span></a></span></p>",
